The paper discusses game theory and mechanism design in the context of cake cutting, which suggests that it would likely fall under the category of cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science). Additionally, the paper discusses algorithms and efficiency, which could place it in the category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The use of strategic agents and equilibria also suggests a potential fit for cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). Finally, the discussion of allocations and equilibria could also place the paper in the category of cs.EC (Economics and Computation).
